data.description: New construction with so much to offer 4 bedrooms with 2 baths, 2 car garage. This amazing home is so affordable with so many extras for this price you will be blown away. The kitchen has custom knotty alder cabinets, granite countertops , lq walk in pantry, undermount sink and double patio doors in the dining that open to the fences yard. This yard has an auto sprinkle and sod . The large living area has a fireplace to enjoy on those cold winter days, The mst bedroom is isolated and has 2 closets. Come check this out today before it is gone
